# Framework Version Numbers

**API Collection**

Version numbers of the Core Foundation framework.

## Overview

Compare these values to the value of the [doc://com.apple.corefoundation/documentation/CoreFoundation/kCFCoreFoundationVersionNumber] variable to identify on which version of the Core Foundation framework your code is executing.

- **Value Not Found**: Special value returned when a Core Foundation function cannot locate a requested value.
- **Current Framework Version Number**: Current version number of the Core Foundation framework.
